{"tid":1070904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羊國（紐西蘭）　是　主張　本土優先　的　第一個國家","createTime":"2019-03-21T03:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T08:18:34.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdc05fc961669442157050a70e04336c300cf5c","tid":1070904,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2327733924129352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2327733924129352&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=94832694\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2327733924129352</a><br />\n<br />\n講過好多次，紐西蘭副總理 Winston Peters 開咗全世界對中國貿易、炒樓反擊戰嘅第一槍。一上台就 devalue 紐紙，禁外人買樓，勁起居屋，跟住迫到中國全面開放奶類入口。侵侵嘅 American First 口號亦係來自佢個黨 New Zealand First，早咗足足20年。羊國呢，經常領先全世界，例如一個世紀前成為最早普選嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n楊文理:<br />\n20年？<br />\n近年嘅應該係obama彈弓口叫人buy american，trump只係延續<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\nWinston Peters 1993年退出National Party組黨，叫做 New Zealand First。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366699226899488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2366699226899488&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=0df35dea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366699226899488</a><br />\n<br />\n羊國影響力超強。唔止美國總統要炒考聯合政府細黨嘅New Zealand First，連台灣總統都追睇羊國編劇嘅邱吉爾流行作品Darkest Hour。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2307711069464971&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2307711069464971%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3%26theater&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=2fee6ec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2307711069464971&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n中國意圖謀殺羊國麥卡錫教授。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tb2eXiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTb2eXiB.jpg&h=ed9c3979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2210804215822324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2210804215822324&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=1b04a03e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2210804215822324</a><br />\n<br />\n明明羊國先係新麥卡錫嘅發源地。然後某北美國家「情報學術界」小朋友就老屈佢哋對中國滲透無動於衷。依家明明外相、防相、內政相都係「排外」NZ First，警政相係工黨政治世家，屌你仲想點呀。寫一大堆無聊官僚規則呀？人哋小國內閣親力親為架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2134250553477691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2134250553477691&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=afbba5d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2134250553477691</a><br />\n<br />\nDarkest Hour 編劇 Anthony McCarten 係羊國人。我嘅「羊國係西方前瞻」論又添一鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2199080526994693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2199080526994693&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=16c4767d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2199080526994693</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年6月27日 <br />\n<br />\n然後輪到大豆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月24日<br />\n<br />\n袋鼠國：中國攞香港FTA要挾我哋唔好同台灣簽FTA啊，點算好？<br />\n羊阿公：嗱你揸吓佢哋個袋。（揸揸）睇吓，即刻單方面取消奶粉關稅啊。你有啲佢冇又好想要嘅嘢，仲駛乜FTA。<br />\n袋鼠國：醒喎Peter仔，話時話你哋人口仲少過香港！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2059153960987351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2059153960987351&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=72247b48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2059153960987351</a><br />\n<br />\n中國資金去羊國炒樓，結果係點呢？老人政治將呢班白癡洗劫一空，羊國退休長者成最大贏家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2059145497654864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2059145497654864&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=d4806567\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2059145497654864</a><br />\n<br />\n羊國真係領先西方喎 //<br />\n&quot;Peters told reporters on Monday that foreign ownership restrictions would constitute a large part of the talks.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2053165094919571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2053165094919571&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=8d170fa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2053165094919571</a><br />\n<br />\n之前見到練講香港似早期殖民地紐西蘭，我嚇咗一跳，因為我有同樣見解。原來佢都住過羊國，睇來呢點係真理，對兩國歷史有了解嘅人都一定係咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WLgrga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WLgrga.png&h=95b7e2ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0240324b62f6ed4395674a40f6500728d2a8a57a","tid":1070904,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"點解中國意圖謀殺麥卡錫教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好欣賞紐西蘭對支那強硬態度<br />\n反而侵侵仲要顧左顧右"},{"pid":"e807c73397517a41a41621a6e521e2c09785b77c","tid":1070904,"uid":218504,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"本土優先係好事，不過都要睇下自己夠唔夠斤兩。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭搞真係食得屎，本土人hea到出汁。<br />\n<br />\n利申: NZer"},{"pid":"e5f0c38c3efe779c50acf12ae8325468dcec6538","tid":1070904,"uid":218504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"Winston Peter 係一條撚樣，有着數屎忽都可以賣，其實佢唔係真本土。"},{"pid"